  ListEnvelope<{ personId, name, email, roles:number[] }>

ERRORS (stderr, exit non-zero)
  400  Unknown role           → use a role from @ibetoni/constants ROLE_TYPEID_BY_NAME
  401  Token expired          → ib auth refresh
  403  Permission denied      → check auth.page.person.read
  500  Backend error          → retry with --verbose

EXAMPLES
  ib person list --role driver
  ib person list --asiakas 1349 --limit 50
"
`;

